data.description: Welcome to 823 N Pennsylvania, a spacious 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom home with 1,425 sqft mol of potential waiting to be unleashed. Stepping inside, you'll immediately notice the enduring charm of the beautiful hardwood floors, ripe for restoration and refinement. With not one but two living rooms, this space offers ample room for creative customization, allowing you to tailor it to your unique lifestyle. The recently refreshed bathroom introduces a contemporary touch while still inviting your personal style. Beyond the living areas, the property also provides the essential feature of a storm shelter, ensuring safety and peace of mind during inclement weather. This home presents a remarkable canvas for your imaginative vision to transform this house into your dream home—a sanctuary that reflects your taste and aspirations, ready to be cherished for years to come.
